Reference:
-----------

https://www.rosehosting.com/blog/install-and-configure-tinyproxy/



1. Installation:
----------------

sudo apt-get install tinyproxy



2. Configuration:
-------------------
open /etc/tinyproxy.conf with root user or [sudo permission] in nano or vim editor..

sudo nano /etc/tinyproxy.conf

update following...

Allow 127.0.0.1
Allow your.local.ip.address


3. run Tiny Proxy Server
--------------------------

sudo /etc/init.d/tinyproxy restart





